ide.com.hk&d=cw67THcQ8%2BNa%2BfcBlgGHU8txnk%2BhbBpP3j1S%2FgfPRD4%3D&h=125120ba\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">到我們的網站www.help4suicide.com.hk</a>。 那裡有一些勵志故事和有趣短片，你可以隨心看看。你也可以進入網站內的『Chat窿』（星期一至五：上午六時至凌晨一時；星期六、日及公眾假期：下午８時至凌晨１時），讓我們的義工為你加油打氣！<br />\n <br />\n我們願意聆聽你的心聲，伴你一起走過這段艱難的時候！只因『晴天雨天要樂天，難關難過總會過』！<br />\n<br />\n《自殺．自療．互助舍》"},{"pid":"0749c691611c52e6210e1cb10cc405d6e2613cb0","tid":1468972,"uid":41411,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:42:35.000Z","msg":"其實相信大部分人都有<br />\n想做其他事分下心 都係完全唔work<br />\n情緒又會低落 瞓得差"},{"pid":"52e92445d2e0c57f6f14abbc14c52318d5f1a7ea","tid":1468972,"uid":295218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:46:45.000Z","msg":"我班連登仔，我係鬼都忍唔住岀嚟笑柒你<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1470387\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1470387</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"fe895048f9bd93171a272ae7518bc8540d69f9e9","tid":1468972,"uid":270733,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-14T09:46:57.000Z","msg":"轉貨幣戰或罷買戰，和理非優勢，請高人指點"},{"pid":"175bf41ec3071e9785dbf2a9246155ccc705ab04","tid":1468972,"uid":8086,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T08:55:12.000Z","msg":"有朋友義教瑜伽，學呼吸法放鬆同幫助訓教<br />\n有興趣tg: sita123"},{"pid":"073a3216a04aa25f24241e134cd0f5c2d2b021e2","tid":1468972,"uid":113155,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-15T09:00:03.000Z","msg":"唔止你，我哋哩啲和理非都係"},{"pid":"c338cba8d67311ec23ffeab30fde716ecc544e77","tid":1468972,"uid":65912,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-17T05:59:19.000Z","msg":"psycho情緒支援tg gp<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1479899\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1479899</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n各位入黎傾傾"}]}